reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 29, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I have found nothing to dislike about this handbag. I am a smaller woman and carrying huge handbags has proven difficult for me. I just don't like them. this is perfect for my stature and holds enough to keep me going through the day. It holds my bifold wallet, keys, sunglasses, cellphone in a case and has a comfortable strap for over the shoulder carrying ease. I went to the grocery store yesterday and the purse comfortably stayed on my shoulder through the shopping trim never slipping off even once. It's 'plain' enough for everyday, but 'dressy' enough for church on Sunday. I may purchase another in a different color.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 5, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I purchased the black purse and absolutely love it! I am able to fit everything needed inside, including my phone. I cannot wait to get my hands on the other colors. I will definitely purchase again.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 24, 2022
reviews.reviewText: Overall the bag is very stylish it's great. Super similar copycat to a small chanel crossbody at literally like 100th of the price. I mean. Obviously not Chanel quality, but for what it is I like it a lot. You can't really complain for the price. My only problem with it is the quilting was not properly aligned around the lock pictured so it looks like a poor counterfeit of itself. Most of the bags other girls got look perfectly symetrically aligned, so I ordered a replacement which will be in a few days so I can update if it's actually as nice as pictured which I think it will be(:One thing I would add is small unobtrusive button clasps around the bottom edges to make the bag more slim and chic but expandable when need be, but I can easily add those myself!
